results.name: Number of divisors of totient of n.
link: Harry J. Smith, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..2000
example: The number of divisors of phi(n) can be greater than, less than, or equal to the number of divisors of n:
program: (PARI) { for (n=1, 2000, write("b062821.txt", n, " ", numdiv(eulerphi(n))) ) } \\ _Harry J. Smith_, Aug 11 2009
